settings.title: Complete freedom in design & customization
settings.desc: We allow you complete control over the design and development product - in order to create a product that correctly conveys your brand. Our product design studio works with you to transform your brand vision into a remarkable vaping experience. Whether you have an in-house team and require basic guidance or you need us to design the entire product from start to finish - we got you covered.

settings.title: Complete Testing Protocol
settings.desc: Before your product is mass-produced, we work closely with your team to ensure that the hardware you selected is a good fit for your process and most importantly - your concentrate. To ensure this, our client services team works with you to implement a rigorous testing protocol and gather any feedback that will allow us to perfect the end product for your specific application.

settings.title: Atomizer
settings.desc: An “atomizer” used to refer to the coil of any vape tank, the part that is responsible for vaporizing e-liquid.

settings.title: Clearomizer
settings.desc: Clearomizers usually comprise of a glass or plastic clear tank, a replaceable coil, a chimney, and a mouthpiece.

settings.title: cartomizer
settings.desc: A cartomizer is a vaping device that attaches to the end of a battery. They are also commonly referred to as cigalikes or just e-cigarettes.
